<p>Someone wrote a new comment on a thread that you once joined.</p>

<%= image_tag @comment.ziltag.photo.image, style: 'max-width:100px;max-height:100px;' %>

<p><%= @comment.username %>: <q><%= @comment.content %></q></p>

<p><%= link_to 'Visit the thread!', photo_path(slug: @comment.ziltag.photo.slug, ziltag_slug: @comment.ziltag.slug) %></p>